      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "23:38"
    },
    {
      "content": "这做起来很简单",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "23:38"
    },
    {
      "content": "但我觉得这反而没有那么真诚",
