      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "23:40"
    },
    {
      "content": "真的吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "23:40"
    },
    {
      "content": "你是第一个说我冷漠的人",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "23:40"
    },
    {
      "content": "怎么了一直没回",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "23:55",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "真的是因为我太冷漠，又伤害到你了吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "23:55"
    },
    {
      "content": "没有，刚才有点emo",
